'''''Skeleton Coast''''' ni filime y’intambara y’abacanshuro yo muri 1987 yakozwe na John Cardos muri firime eshatu za mbere kuri producer Harry Alan Towers . Nibwo bwambere muri Towers 'Breton Film Productions<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film246859.html</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Mugihe cy'intambara yo muri [[Angola]] umukozi wa CIA Michael Smith akorana ninyeshyamba za UNITA<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=186805.html</ref>. Yafashwe n’ingabo za [[Angola]], yoherezwa muri gereza kugira ngo abazwe n’umudage w’iburasirazuba witwa Major Schneider<ref>https://www.troma.com/films/skeleton-coast/</ref>. Se wa Smith, Koloneli Bill Smith wahoze mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru Colonel Bill Smith ntabwo yizera leta ya [[Amerika]] kurekura umuhungu we<ref>https://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/90370/skeleton-coast</ref>. Koloneli yagiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo y'uburengerazuba]] aho yishyuye Elia amayobera kugirango amenye amakuru yukuri kubyerekeye umuhungu we aho yari ari imbohe<ref>https://www.radiotimes.com/movie-guide/b-mo8fj6/skeleton-coast/</ref>. Colonel Smith aha akazi abacanshuro barindwi azajyana muri [[Angola]] gutabara umuhungu we<ref>https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/africa/mad-max-and-namibia-s-skeleton-coast-movie-magic-wilderness-10252467.html</ref>.

Kapiteni Simpson, umuyobozi w’inzego zishinzwe umutekano z’ikirombe cya diyama afite umugabo uhanze amaso Coloneli atinya ko ashobora kuba akora magendu ya diyama<ref>https://www.moviemeter.nl/film/34937</ref>. Umugore wa Elia, Opal akomeje kugirana umubano utemewe na Simpson amumenyesha ko Coloneli yishe umuntu w’umutekano we<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Skeleton_Coast/11282514</ref>, mu byukuri yishwe na Rick Weston, umuyobozi w’ingabo bwite za Smith<ref>https://mondo-esoterica.net/Skeleton%20Coast.html</ref>. Rick yamenyesheje Coloneli ko yari umukozi wibanga wa [[Angola]]. Elia yahise amenya ko Col. Smith yamwishyuye amafaranag yamiganano<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/81351-skeleton-coast</ref>. Binjiye muri Angola, abacanshuro bafatanya na Sekassi, umuyobozi wo mu bwoko bwa Jonas Savimbi w’inyeshyamba kugira ngo bashyigikire gutabara Michael Smith<ref>https://filmfront.no/utgivelse/45669/skeleton-coast</ref>.

